N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4205.3 - Fee refunds

State Regulations

Within one year from the date of payment and upon the
audit of the State Comptroller, the Department of State may refund any fee paid
for which no license is issued or refund that portion of the payment that is in
excess of the amount prescribed therefor. Notes
